Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.23,0:00:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit is married?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.34,0:00:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he’s the one with Rahayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.63,0:00:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He's Inggit's husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.82,0:00:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.59,0:00:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have a reason to refuse\Nthis arranged marriage,...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.95,0:00:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a reason to accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.23,0:00:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I made you breakfast.\NTempeh bacem and bacem tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.82,0:00:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You still want to get an A, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.04,0:00:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to be angry with you,\Nyou know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.34,0:00:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,(Previously)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If something's wrong, you can tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.07,0:00:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.66,0:01:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about Tristan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.56,0:01:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Arya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.47,0:01:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he's old enough\Nto take care of himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.33,0:01:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can give you my suggestion,...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.54,0:01:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe it's best\Nthat you focus on your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.87,0:01:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She needs you a lot more right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.22,0:01:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay? That's my suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.98,0:01:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.80,0:01:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.00,0:01:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen.\NRegarding the learning materials,...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.47,0:01:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,right now,\NI have family matters to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.30,0:01:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be a little late.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.22,0:01:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try to be back on schedule\Nnext week. It should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.10,0:01:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll try. Yes. Okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.75,0:02:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, you're not resting?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.34,0:02:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit, Arya. I want to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.79,0:02:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.34,0:02:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-Inggit.\N-Yes, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.00,0:02:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here, Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.67,0:02:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's time for the two of you\Nto go back to Jakarta.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, Mom. How can we leave you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.67,0:02:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You've stayed with me long enough here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.63,0:02:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm stronger now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I honestly don't mind staying here\Nwith you for a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.59,0:02:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The same with Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.38,0:02:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that you need Inggit\Nto be close to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Arya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.96,0:03:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that you really care about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.84,0:03:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think it's time\Nthat we all get back to our own lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that Inggit's dad\Nagrees with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.92,0:03:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay? Go on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.46,0:04:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,♪You are supposed to lecture me♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♪But then you stopped and looked at me♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.19,0:04:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I still can't believe\NHow far you could see♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.93,0:04:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,♪All of the care that you displayed♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.27,0:04:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,♪All of the charming things\NThat you said♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.58,0:04:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Somehow made me think\NThat we are meant to be♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.26,0:04:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,♪You make me feel every love in me♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.90,0:04:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,♪You let me heal from my history♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.15,0:04:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Now you have found your way\NInto my heart to stay♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Your passion in me♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.68,0:04:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Has turned out to be♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.39,0:05:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,♪The reason\NThat I've been made complete♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,=My Lecturer My Husband=
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.41,0:05:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamarind Soup\Nwas your dad's favorite food.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Once he made me promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that I’d only cook with a happy heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So that our food would be delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.41,0:05:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Dad really hate\Nwhen he sees us sad or down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree with him, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.94,0:05:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very important to remember\Nsomething happy about someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.77,0:05:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially if it's about cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopefully I can stay true to his words.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:05:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm going to cook,\NI have to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.89,0:06:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're his favorite son-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.18,0:06:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course he is. He’s the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.81,0:06:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink some water.\NYou haven't had any all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-Thank you.\N-Why did you only get one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.60,0:06:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.56,0:06:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-Do you want me to help you?\N-No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-Come sit.\N-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.77,0:06:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.47,0:06:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that for?\NYou're going to eat two?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.81,0:06:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-Enjoy your food.\N-Enjoy your food.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.23,0:07:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I still don't have the heart\Nto leave Mom here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.23,0:07:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just stay here. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What about your work?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.18,0:07:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I can work on the learning material\Nfrom here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.10,0:07:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All I need to do is send it.\NI can take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.71,0:07:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you can go back first.\NI'll stay here with Mom for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.98,0:07:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.93,0:08:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to go back to Jakarta\Nor do you want me to stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just feel bad\Nbecause of your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.64,0:08:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.60,0:08:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So, do you want us\Nto go back or to stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just go back to Jakarta together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.31,0:08:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.39,0:08:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.14,0:08:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I just keep thinking about it because\Nlosing Dad must be rough for Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.18,0:08:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's definitely rough for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.06,0:08:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Losing someone that we love\Nis very rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.43,0:09:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever lost someone\Nthat you love?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.85,0:09:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Does "not yet" mean you will?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.18,0:09:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What else haven't I packed yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.39,0:09:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you haven't packed the soap yet.\NIt's in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.02,0:09:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-Right.\N-Do you want me to help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.68,0:09:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.94,0:10:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys go ahead inside the house.\NI'll get the suitcase.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.31,0:11:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Tristan knows that you're married.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.97,0:11:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The others already know too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-How did they know?\N-Well,...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.51,0:11:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Tristan went to Yogyakarta.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.64,0:11:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.51,0:11:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that Mr. Arya saw him too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Arya didn't tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.85,0:11:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.43,0:11:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'll go home now, okay?\N-Thanks, Iim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.97,0:12:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-Be careful on your way back.\N-I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.51,0:12:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Arya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.81,0:12:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Arya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.56,0:12:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? Iim already left?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.84,0:12:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know\Nthat Tristan came to Yogyakarta?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw Tristan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Arya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Arya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew that Tristan came\Nto Yogyakarta, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.63,0:12:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know Tristan came to Yogyakarta.\NI saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.00,0:12:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And I saw him quietly standing there.\NHe stood there, looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.96,0:12:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at you. Looking at your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.30,0:12:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-You're just telling me now?\N-Not that I wanted to tell you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.71,0:12:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-I already knew...\N-When were you going to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.09,0:12:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-I asked you and you just answered me.\N-I was waiting for the right time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,When's the right time, Arya?\NI asked you and you just answered me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-Inggit, listen.\N-Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:13:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Your situation at that time\Ndidn't allow for me to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-How did you know my situation...\N-Because I could see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.00,0:13:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm your husband, so I know.\N-All you did was see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-Did you feel what I feel?\N-I know what I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.99,0:13:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-How did you know?\N-And when's the right time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-How did you know?\N-And yesterday wasn't the right time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.53,0:13:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And if he was doing the right thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.65,0:13:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know\Nit wasn't the right time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.83,0:13:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't he meet you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he came to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.78,0:13:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-and say he's sorry for your loss?\N-That's not my question, Arya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking why you didn't tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-That's it.\N-It's not I didn't want to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.45,0:13:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-So, why?\N-I already said I was waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's sit and talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.55,0:13:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-Why didn't you tell me?\N-Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.11,0:13:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't I tell you right away\Nwhen I saw him there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.03,0:13:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't tell you right away?\NBecause I thought it wasn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-That's what you thought.\N-Listen to me first. You were grieving.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.03,0:13:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yeah, but that's what you thought.\N-And I would have added another burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How would you know that if you told me\Nyou'd have added another burden for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.56,0:13:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How would you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.25,0:13:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-Did you ever discuss it with me?\N-No, my question now is this…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-I knew that you were worried...\N-When I went through all that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.65,0:13:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He came there, he didn't meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.82,0:13:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-Arya!\N-Whose problem is that? Ask him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.45,0:13:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-Don't ask me.\N-Why should I ask him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.03,0:14:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I'm asking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time,\Nwhile I was going through all that,...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.63,0:14:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,did you ever asked me how I felt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you ever ask me to discuss it\Nwith you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.96,0:14:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You never asked me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You only say\N"I know what's best for you."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-"I know what's best for you."\N-I know what's best for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.63,0:14:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-So what's my purpose here?\N-And no matter what...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.09,0:14:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm your husband and I'm older than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.34,0:14:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, my purpose here\Nis just to follow what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my husband, so I have\Nto always listen to what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You will never ask me how I feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.88,0:14:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you even care about how I feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.13,0:14:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Or do you actually only care\Nabout yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I can decide\Nthat I want to meet Tristan right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.59,0:14:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And I won't ask for your permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's up to you if you want to say\N"I'm your husband, Inggit".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.71,0:14:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever. Because I’ve never felt\Nthat I was treated like your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.29,0:14:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, why should I ask\Nfor your permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-What are you doing?\N-I want to discuss my grades, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.50,0:15:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any time. I'm busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.34,0:15:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You know where the door is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.59,0:15:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you getting angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just giving my opinion\Nthat the bakwan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.71,0:15:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,starting from its texture,\Nisn't crunchy enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.29,0:15:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's too salty.\NIt's like a fake bakwan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.79,0:15:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it suits you.\NA fake bakwan for a fake husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.00,0:15:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of waiting\Nfor something unclear,...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.88,0:15:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,just choose what's clear\Nright in front of your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that my feelings might\Nnot be important to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You would never understand\Nbecause you don't have a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to try so hard\Nto be a good husband to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.71,0:15:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my mom and dad's ideal\Nson-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.00,0:15:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to go through the trouble\Nof trying so hard to win my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.17,0:15:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to change my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.46,0:16:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Prof, good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-Have you seen Tristan?\N-I haven't seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-Have you seen Tristan?\N-Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.67,0:16:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Dave. You're Dave, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.54,0:16:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yeah. Inggit.\N-Yeah, it's Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.13,0:16:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-You can just go ahead.\N-Okay. I’ll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Dave, do you know where Tristan is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.21,0:16:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I called him but his phone isn't active.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Dave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.67,0:16:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-I don't know where he is, Inggit.\N-There's no way you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.17,0:16:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're his best friend and his roommate.\NHow could you not know where he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.59,0:17:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What I know is that he's feeling\Nreally down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.03,0:17:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Where is he?\NI want to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.75,0:17:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you did to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.29,0:17:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to the point that he wants to move away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.75,0:17:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Move away? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.29,0:17:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know where he is, Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.04,0:17:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.63,0:17:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,he doesn't want to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.17,0:17:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Good bye, Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.88,0:18:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.75,0:18:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Inggit, listen to me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.29,0:18:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I need to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to do this. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to Iim's house.\NI'm going to live there for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm also going to look for Tristan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.42,0:18:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Look for Tristan?\NWhy do you have to live...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me first. Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.54,0:18:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Don't be childish, Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.84,0:18:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We can talk about this properly.\NListen to me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.92,0:18:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.54,0:18:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop. Listen to me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:18:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone needs to leave this house,\Nit should be me. Not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.67,0:19:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your house, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.79,0:19:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'll leave.\N-Yes, this is my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.04,0:19:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But have I ever had a place here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.94,0:19:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you listen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.71,0:19:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If you leave now to see Tristan,\Nto look for Tristan,...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll think that you chose him\Nover our marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.54,0:19:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.59,0:19:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.46,0:19:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm allowed to have a choice now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.59,0:19:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit. Wait, listen to me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.67,0:19:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.34,0:19:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait and listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:19:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me take you\Nto where you can meet Tristan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,At least give me a chance\Nto make sure that you'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you to where you can meet him.\NI know where Tristan is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.42,0:20:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I talked to Professor Gunawan.\NI know where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.53,0:20:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You can meet him and it's up to you\Nwhat you want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.07,0:20:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I will wait for you.\NBut let me take you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.43,0:20:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.44,0:20:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.94,0:20:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get the car keys. We'll go.\NI'll take you there, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.86,0:20:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-Good evening, sir.\N-Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.57,0:20:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Excuse me. I want to ask something.\N-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.24,0:20:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I get\Nto the Jayagiri community health clinic?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still far from here.\NIt's at the top of a hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The roads are steep too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.89,0:20:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous to go there late\Nat night like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.60,0:21:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you go there in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.27,0:21:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a hotel near here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.14,0:21:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There is. Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.39,0:21:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-Okay. Thank you, sir.\N-Yes, you're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.75,0:21:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.22,0:21:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The community health clinic is still far\Nand the road is dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay if we stay at a hotel\Nfor tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.12,0:21:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's over there, right?\N-Yes, go straight and to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.85,0:21:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.75,0:22:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Arya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.85,0:22:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.18,0:22:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.18,0:22:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-You're lying.\N-Of course I'm lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.27,0:22:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I answered you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.22,0:22:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.85,0:22:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you doing all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.56,0:22:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming all the away from Jakarta.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.77,0:23:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasting your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.02,0:23:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to take me to meet Tristan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.52,0:23:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that you're doing all this\Nfor me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.56,0:23:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.02,0:23:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why doesn't it make sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.64,0:23:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.52,0:23:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think a husband\Nwould let his wife be with another man.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.18,0:24:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.00,0:24:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,who told me that this marriage\Nwasn't a real marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.06,0:24:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to know my real reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.68,0:24:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a promise to your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.22,0:24:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A promise that I still hold onto\Nto this day...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.10,0:24:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that I would put your happiness\Nover mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.27,0:24:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think... Yes.\NYour happiness is being with Tristan.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.84,0:25:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So, by doing this, I'm only trying\Nto keep true to my promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.02,0:25:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Arya.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.68,0:25:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.84,0:25:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That time, you told me that you\Nhad your reasons for marrying me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.39,0:25:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.43,0:26:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you remember\Nyour seventh birthday,...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.44,0:26:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,your dad's friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.47,0:26:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,brought his kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.87,0:26:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.97,0:26:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, it had only been a year\Nsince the kid's mom left him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.13,0:26:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And he really felt the loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.26,0:26:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Not long after that,\Nhis dad was married again.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.84,0:26:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He lost his smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.34,0:26:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He lost his happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.26,0:26:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And then that kid met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.43,0:27:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And that changed his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.80,0:27:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,For the first time, Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.76,0:27:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That kid could smile again.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.42,0:27:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He found his happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.64,0:27:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, you became my student.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.22,0:27:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I did not want to throw away\Nthat chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.80,0:27:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter the risks.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.40,0:27:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I have been in love with you\Nsince back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.88,0:27:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I met you at the campus.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.23,0:27:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But again...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.02,0:27:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,your happiness is above everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.56,0:28:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Hate is an easy thing to say♪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.69,0:28:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Spoken when your heart is in doubt♪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.86,0:29:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Doubts that arise out of fear♪
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.00,0:29:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♪An unrequited love♪
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.15,0:29:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♪You and I are false images♪
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.61,0:29:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Of a successful happy relationships♪
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.01,0:29:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.76,0:29:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to check if Tristan is up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.30,0:29:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,♪The further I go to leave you behind♪
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.82,0:29:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I'm getting closer to you instead♪
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.52,0:30:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-Excuse me. Is Tristan here?\N-Yes, Tristan's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.15,0:30:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'll go get him.\N-Sure. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.17,0:30:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Tristan.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.47,0:30:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Tristan.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.80,0:30:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit's here and she wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.05,0:30:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she wants to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.05,0:31:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to wait here?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.63,0:31:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything, Arya.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.11,0:31:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.76,0:31:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.63,0:32:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to explain everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.59,0:32:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How it ended up this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.47,0:32:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the right\Nto know about it directly from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.22,0:32:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.67,0:32:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.84,0:32:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought about what I should say.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.22,0:32:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What words should come out of my mouth\Nwhen I saw you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.38,0:32:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of different words.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.34,0:32:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A variety of sentences.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.34,0:32:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,About the feeling of regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.46,0:33:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.88,0:33:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And longing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.67,0:33:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.71,0:33:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.67,0:33:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And what came to me\Nwas just one word, Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.62,0:33:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.90,0:33:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry that I wasn't by your side\Nwhen you needed me the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.57,0:33:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to apologize to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.86,0:33:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know. I should ask myself\Nfor forgiveness, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.77,0:34:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of my behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.57,0:34:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.52,0:34:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost the most important person\Nin my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.40,0:34:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And I didn't even know\Nif I would ever see her again or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.57,0:34:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sure that you lost me?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.27,0:34:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.11,0:34:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a couple of minutes ago, Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.32,0:34:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,When I saw the way you looked\Nat Mr. Arya.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.45,0:35:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Learn from my mistakes, okay, Inggit?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.20,0:35:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be too late to confess your love.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.82,0:36:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.99,0:36:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.39,0:36:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.70,0:36:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.24,0:36:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.03,0:36:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? What's wrong? Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.32,0:36:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait. Why are you running?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.95,0:36:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit, can't you stop first\Nand then we talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.72,0:36:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit. No. Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.68,0:36:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-What is it?\N-Arya, who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.65,0:36:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're obviously\Nthe daughter of your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.99,0:36:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.57,0:36:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're my wife\Nif I'm still allowed to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.11,0:36:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-Really?\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.28,0:36:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How come I never felt like\NI was treated as a wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.36,0:36:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-Can we not fight about that here?\N-I don't want to fight about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.28,0:37:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to tell you that I never\Nfelt like I was treated as a wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.44,0:37:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still my lecturer.\NI'm still your student.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.44,0:37:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't feel like\Nwe're husband and wife at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.07,0:37:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen. I'll explain. Can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.82,0:37:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.90,0:37:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt that I only wanted\Nto guide you...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.19,0:37:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-Guide?\N-To teach...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.53,0:37:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Teach? Is that a lecturer or a husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.86,0:37:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just wanted you to become better.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.90,0:37:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you don't believe that I can decide\Nwhat's best for myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.15,0:37:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't believe\Nthat I can be an adult. Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.24,0:37:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that I don't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.15,0:37:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-But...\N-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.32,0:37:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Arya.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.19,0:37:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen. Ever since I was little,\Nand even until now,...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.74,0:37:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I was never given the chance\Nto be an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.07,0:37:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,All of the decisions in my life\Nwere made by my mom and dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.82,0:37:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after we got married,...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.65,0:37:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,everything at home\Nhas to be what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.86,0:37:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when we're fighting,...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.15,0:37:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,you told me to memorize\Nthe learning materials first.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.94,0:37:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What does the materials\Nhave to do with learning?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.49,0:37:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.40,0:38:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.94,0:38:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.86,0:38:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. That's good that you admitted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.40,0:38:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Say sorry first.\NDon't let it be me all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.32,0:38:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm sorry.\N-Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.44,0:38:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I talked to Tristan.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.53,0:38:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And I decided something\Nthat is my choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.32,0:38:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.82,0:38:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And I decided...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.11,0:38:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,to love Arya.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.40,0:38:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my choice.\NI mean, I can choose now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.19,0:38:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So, okay. My choice is to love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.03,0:38:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's up to you if you want to love me...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.49,0:39:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I have one question.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.74,0:39:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-Okay.\N-Okay. This is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.94,0:39:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-Listen.\N-Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.90,0:39:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you relax your face?\NWe're husband and wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.03,0:39:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-What did we just do? We just...\N-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.65,0:39:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-Then relax your face.\N-Yeah. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.69,0:39:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,From all the way there,\Nyou were running, making me panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.82,0:39:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What was your reason for coming here?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.44,0:40:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking for network signal. Look.\NI got the signal here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.44,0:40:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-To do what?\N-To...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.32,0:40:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,To send this.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.90,0:40:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.44,0:40:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we pose more\Nlike a husband and wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.44,0:40:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No...\NDo you not want to kiss me?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.57,0:40:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine if you don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.69,0:40:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'm going to send it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.57,0:40:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,To everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.19,0:40:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My husband...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.61,0:40:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.39,0:40:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.82,0:40:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.15,0:40:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.32,0:40:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-Oh, my God.\N-Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.03,0:40:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-They're for real.\N-So cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.19,0:41:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.15,0:41:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at their faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.07,0:41:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They look so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.88,0:41:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Life at first feels\NAs beautiful as I imagined♪
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.21,0:41:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Until you came\NAnd disturbed this feeling♪
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.24,0:41:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Nothing was ever wrong\NThere were no problems♪
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.75,0:41:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Until you came and ruined it♪
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.54,0:42:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I hate you♪
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.29,0:42:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,♪But my heart chooses love♪
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.60,0:42:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Need to get away♪
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.98,0:42:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Erase all traces of you♪
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.31,0:42:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,♪But life puts us together♪
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.00,0:42:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,♪You and I♪
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.27,0:42:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Happy♪
